<hymn_number>1266</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 xī biān de kuàng yě lǐ yǒu yī zhǐ mí shī de yáng jī è liú lí piāo dàng
 hēi yè lái lín bào fēng yǔ xià jiàng xiǎo yáng jiāng yào qù hé fāng
 zhǔ hū zhào wǒ men qù xún zhǎo mí shī de yáng wǒ men zǎo yǐ bèi qǐ le xíng náng
 zǒu guò chūn qiū dōng xià zǒu guò yī gè gè shān gǎng yīn xiǎo yáng zài wǒ men de xīn shàng
 xī běi gāo yuán de fēng shā xī běi gāo yuán de xuě huā dǎng bù zhù wǒ men qián jìn de bù fá
 xī běi gāo yuán de fēng shā xī běi gāo yuán de xuě huā yān méi bù le wǒ men duì xiǎo yáng de qiān guà</lyrics>
<title>xī biān de kuàng yě lǐ yǒu yī zhǐ mí shī de yáng 迦南1266</title>
</song>